title: How to Install a K&N Air Intake (Part #69-8619TS)
description: Follow these simple steps to add up to 6.7 hp and 5.5 lb. ft. of torque to your 2013 Subaru BRZ, 2013-2014 Scion FR-S 2.0L or 2012-2013 Toyota GT86 2.0L.

asset.title: 2013 Subaru BRZ / 2013 & 2014 Scion FR-S 2.0L / 2012 & 2013 2013 Toyota GT86 Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2013 Subaru BRZ, 2013 - 2014 Scion FR-S 2.0L and the 2012-2013 Toyota GT86 2.0L 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-8619TS

This intake system created an estimated gain of 6.7 horsepower at 6,670 RPM and 5.5 lb. ft. of torque at 5,670 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. 

Visit the product page to see an up to date list of vehicle models this air intake fits.

http://www.KNfilters.com

K&N 69-8619TS fits:
2014 SCION FR-S 2.0L H4 
2013 TOYOTA GT86 2.0L H4 
2013 SUBARU BRZ 2.0L H4 
2013 SCION FR-S 2.0L H4 
2012 TOYOTA GT86 2.0L H4
